      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Susan Park was appointed Director General, Operations at the Department for Work and Pensions in April 2018. Previously she had been Director General, Universal Credit Operations.</p>

<p>Susan rejoined the Department for Work and Pensions in 2012 as the Group Director for the Child Maintenance Group, having spent the previous 4 years as Corporate Affairs Director for a Non-Departmental Public Body.</p>

<p>Other roles within the Department for Work and Pensions include:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Principal Private Secretary to 4 Secretaries of State</li>
  <li>Work Services Director</li>
</ul>
</div>
      </section>

      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_4721">
            <h1 id="director-general-operations">Director General, Operations </h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>The Director General, Operations is responsible for:</p>

<ul>
  <li>delivering public services for the Department for Work and Pensions</li>
  <li>providing services to promote parental responsibilities (including family-based arrangements) and managing the statutory child maintenance scheme</li>
</ul>
</div>
            <div class="read-more">
                <p class="js-hide-other-departments organisations-name-list">
  <a class="organisation-link" href="/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions">Department for Work and Pensions</a>
</p>

            </div>
</section>      </div>

